<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
     <meta charset="UTF-8" />
     <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
     <title>Message Sent</title>
     <style>
          body {
               margin: 0;
               font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
               background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1d3557, #457b9d);
               min-height: 100vh;
               display: flex;
               justify-content: center;
               align-items: center;
          }

          .card {
               width: 420px;
               background: #fff;
               border-radius: 14px;
               box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, .25);
               padding: 32px 28px;
               text-align: center;
          }

          .check {
               width: 64px;
               height: 64px;
               margin: 0 auto 16px;
               border-radius: 50%;
               background: #eaf4fb;
               display: flex;
               align-items: center;
               justify-content: center;
               font-size: 34px;
               color: #1d3557;
          }

          h1 {
               margin: 4px 0 8px;
               font-size: 22px;
               color: #1d3557;
          }

          p {
               margin: 0 0 20px;
               color: #555;
               font-size: 14px;
          }

          .btn {
               display: inline-block;
               background: #1d3557;
               color: #fff;
               text-decoration: none;
               padding: 12px 18px;
               border-radius: 8px;
               font-weight: 600;
               transition: .25s;
          }

          .btn:hover {
               background: #457b9d;
               transform: translateY(-1px);
          }

          .sub {
               margin-top: 10px;
               font-size: 12px;
               color: #7a7a7a;
          }
     </style>
</head>

<body>
     <div class="card">
          <div class="check">✓</div>
          <h1>Message Sent</h1>
          <p>Thanks for contacting us. We’ll get back to you shortly.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/">Back to Home</a>
     </div>
</body>

</html>